headline: Assessing Republic Services (RSG) Valuation After New Renewable Natural Gas Facility Milestone
summary: Republic Services (RSG) is back in focus after the company and Ameresco reported successful operation of a renewable natural gas facility in Illinois, turning landfill gas into pipeline-quality fuel with significant projected emissions cuts. headline: AI Is Being Used to Find Valuable Commodities in Our Trash
summary: The White House’s push to boost domestic production of raw materials has turned attention to America’s waste stream.
